---
const stats = [
  {
    name: 'Years',
    value: '25',
  },
  {
    name: 'Experts',
    value: '3',
  },
  {
    name: 'Projects',
    value: '1000+',
  },
  {
    name: 'Awards',
    value: "'3'",
  },
];
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">
      <img
        class="mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-xl rounded-3xl"
        width="576"
        height="864"
        src="/assets/slate-sml.webp"
        alt="Top rated Gold Coast slate tiling experts - slate tiles for a fair price"
      />
      <img
        class="mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-xl rounded-3xl"
        width="576"
        height="864"
        src="/assets/slate-tile-sml.webp"
        alt="Top rated Gold Coast slate tiling experts - slate tiles for a fair price"
      />
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <!-- Mission description -->
        <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Gold Coast Stone Tiling Experts</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">Golden Tiling's Slate Tiling Services</h3>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              Welcome to Golden Tiling, where we invite you to explore the rustic charm and enduring appeal of slate tiling. 
              Our slate tiling services on the Gold Coast are designed to infuse your indoor and outdoor spaces with a touch 
              of natural beauty and robust durability. With a dedication to craftsmanship and a passion for creating spaces 
              that stand the test of time, Golden Tiling is your trusted partner for transforming ordinary areas into extraordinary 
              showcases of slate's unique character.
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">The Unmatched Allure of Slate</h3>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              Slate, with its rugged textures and rich earthy tones, brings a unique and captivating aesthetic to any space. 
              At Golden Tiling, we specialize in the art of slate tiling, offering a wide variety of slate types and patterns 
              that allow you to create a distinctive look that suits your style. Whether you're envisioning a cozy fireplace 
              surround, a durable outdoor patio, or a rustic kitchen floor, our team of tiling experts ensures that each slate 
              tile is meticulously placed to enhance both aesthetics and functionality.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 mt-20">
        

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
          <!-- Mission description -->
          <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight">Quality and Endurance</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
                Our commitment to quality is unwavering. We source the finest slate materials, and our skilled professionals 
                utilize cutting-edge techniques to ensure every tile installation is flawless. The result? Spaces that not 
                only radiate beauty but also withstand the rigors of daily use and the Gold Coast's dynamic climate. When 
                you choose Golden Tiling for your slate tiling project, you're choosing excellence, durability, and a connection 
                to nature's enduring elegance.
              </p>
              <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
                Discover the timeless allure of slate tiling with Golden Tiling. Contact us today to schedule a consultation and 
                experience how our Gold Coast slate tiling services can elevate your spaces, providing lasting beauty and functionality 
                that you'll cherish for years to come.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full">
      <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {
          stats.map((stat) => (
            <div class="border-primary-900/10 dark:border-primary-300/10 rounded-3xl border p-6">
              <dt class="text-base">{stat.name}</dt>
              <dd class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight">{stat.value}</dd>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
